OL,3,CMan, 59, guilty of sexually touching
OL,4,Ctwo girls and making indecent images
OL,6,FA 59-year-old man has been found
OL,7,Fguilty at Jersey's Royal Court on
OL,8,Fseveral counts of sexual touching and
OL,9,Fmaking indecent images of a child.
OL,11,FManuel Amaral Mila will stay in
OL,12,Fcustody and be sentenced at a later
OL,13,Fdate.
OL,15,FThe offences came to light after a
OL,16,Fgirl said she was touched by Mila at
OL,17,Fhis home while he thought she was
OL,18,Fsleeping in March 2023.
