OL,6,FDuring subsequent interviews, Jersey
OL,7,FPolice discovered that something
OL,8,Fsimilar had happened in a separate
OL,9,Fincident to another girl.
OL,11,FMila was arrested and three indecent
OL,12,Fimages of children were found on his
OL,13,Fmobile phone.
OL,15,FHe pled guilty to the pictures but
OL,16,Fmaintained his innocence over the
OL,17,Fthree charges of sexual touching.
OL,19,FHowever, the Court convicted him of
OL,20,Fall charges.
