OL,6,FDetective Constable Carla Garnier from
OL,7,FJersey Police's Public Protection Unit
OL,8,Fsays: "The young victims in this case
OL,9,Fhave shown immense courage in coming
OL,10,Fforward to report these incidents.
OL,12,F"We are committed to investigating and
OL,13,Fprosecuting all sexual offenders and
OL,14,Fencourage anyone who has been the
OL,15,Fvictim of a crime of this nature to
OL,16,Freport it to police."
